Class LinkedListRecursive<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.util.LinkedListRecursive<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - Generic Object of Type E contained within the LinkedList implementation.

    public class LinkedListRecursive<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    Custom implementation of a recursive linked list that doesn't allow for null elements or duplicate elements as defined by Equals().
    Author:
    Steven Mayo
